data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT SELLER IS MOTIVATED!! This All-Brick Waterfront home in the Cedar Grove neighborhood is on over half an acre. Entering you will see beautiful hardwood floors. Great Room has tons of natural light, fireplace & access to waterfront balcony/deck. Eat-in Kitchen features beautiful custom cabinets with lighting, solid surface counters with bar & desk, stainless steel appliances, pantry. Keeping Room & Access to Sunroom overlooking the pond. Master Suite on main has water views and built-ins with vanities & great private bath featuring walk-in closet with built-ins, dual vanity & walk-in shower with bench. Main floor has 2 additional spacious bedrooms, one has built-in desk for an office. Upstairs offers a 4th Bedroom with private full bath. Spacious walkout Basement is perfect for entertaining/man cave with big screen TV, Full Bath, Bedroom 5 & a potential 6th Bedroom. Basement leads out to Fully Fenced Oasis Backyard with multiple patios, outdoor lighting with a fountain, plus an outdoor kitchen. All of this is just minutes from shopping, schools, & Lake Murray!  ** Seller will leave pool table  in basement, brand new garage doors and SELLER IS  MOTIVATED!!
